Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.00,0:00:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（本片开始）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.07,0:00:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚁地狱 离家出走纯情美少女的奸淫日记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人从小一起长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情就像姐妹一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.09,0:00:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中趁暑假时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着父母到东京去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.09,0:00:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光莉在网络上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.10,0:00:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到了一些男网友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.10,0:00:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就住在东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来就想去东京看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.05,0:00:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此男网友说会租房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.12,0:00:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们暑假时去玩几天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.06,0:01:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们父母不会答应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.99,0:01:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们说好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.00,0:01:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人要偷偷去东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.01,0:01:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.01,0:01:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们被骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.08,0:01:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是第一次跟网友见面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.09,0:01:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.09,0:01:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.03,0:01:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.10,0:01:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.03,0:01:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔的嗜好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.04,0:01:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.11,0:01:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.11,0:01:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么光莉会来读东京的大学吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.11,0:02:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.12,0:02:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很努力的想要考上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们努力很久了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.06,0:02:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假很长吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.06,0:02:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们带你们去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.06,0:02:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.08,0:02:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有味道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.02,0:02:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像醉了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.04,0:03:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会带你们到很棒的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.11,0:03:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做很快乐的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.07,0:03:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.01,0:03:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的肉体真棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:03:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我起来没看到人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.05,0:04:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真年轻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.05,0:04:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这是哪里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.12,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.06,0:04:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是我们的性奴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.00,0:04:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.07,0:04:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们租下的这个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租金可是非常昂贵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.01,0:04:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们朋友跑路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.01,0:04:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠下房间的租金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要50万啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.09,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.03,0:05:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不关我们的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被发现的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被父母看到会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大老远过来很累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.01,0:05:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是花了很多钱买小女生的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们挑选出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.09,0:06:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让老大开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要你们开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.04,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭什么哭啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要这么凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.12,0:06:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会让她们更害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.99,0:06:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖听话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假这段时间就好好服侍我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会让父母知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但可以拿钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会很舒服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.02,0:07:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天都做过一发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.09,0:07:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.03,0:07:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么从我们开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.11,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.05,0:07:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.99,0:07:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.08,0:08:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.10,0:08:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.04,0:08:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.04,0:08:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我安分一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.05,0:08:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.99,0:08:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.07,0:09:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来含住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.01,0:09:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憋的难受吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.08,0:09:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用舌头舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.09,0:09:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.09,0:09:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.03,0:09:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.04,0:09:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插得很深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.11,0:09:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴都湿了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.07,0:10:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.07,0:10:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.01,0:10:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.02,0:10:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.09,0:10:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.03,0:10:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.04,0:10:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.11,0:10:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.12,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转过去看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.06,0:11:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.00,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.02,0:11:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都看光了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.10,0:11:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我含住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.04,0:11:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.12,0:12:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.99,0:12:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.07,0:12:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淫穴真棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着含住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.03,0:12:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在抽动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来含住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伺候我们舒服点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.07,0:13:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含得深一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.09,0:13:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.06,0:14:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.06,0:14:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点舔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.07,0:14:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含得深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.08,0:14:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点做啊
